'desc': [u'

Barbie Conditioning Shampoo-Soft & Silky (100 ml) Price: Rs.75

The Barbie Conditioning Shampoo is a mild shampoo that will cleanse your infant’s hair and scalp caringly. The enriched formula used in creating the Barbie Conditioning Shampoo Soft and Silky contains the goodness of silk proteins and Pro vitamin B5.

Pro Vitamin B5 easily penetrates into the scalp and nourishes the hair roots. This makes the hair strong and resilient. Silk protein has the properties with which it helps in retaining the moisture content in the hair and hence makes the hair strong and healthy. Silk protein also helps in conditioning the hair in such a way that the hair strands become more manageable and they get more shine and volume. Using this Barbie Conditioning Shampoo Soft and Silky will help in reducing hair breakage and stimulate the growth of healthy hair that shine with all its vigor. You can use this mild formulation on your tiny tot’s hair and scalp to clean and nourish their delicate scalp and to make their hair lustrous.
